songs.title: Die Alone
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
I dont wanna die, without her
I dont wanna die, without her
I just wanna die, i just wanna die, with you
Shorty On My Mind
Shorty On my mind
I dont wanna die alone
I dont wanna die alone
I just wanna die, i just wanna die, with you
Shorty On My Mind
Shorty On my mind
I dont wanna die alone
I dont wanna die alone
